{"article_id":"zBCh8BNfUdo8nGmk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"New Week , Same Argument :","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Romney , Obama & Who 's Being Dishonest","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"President Obama and his campaign are being `` dishonest ''","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"when they attack his record as a business executive ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Republican presidential candidate Mitt Romney said this morning on Fox & Friends","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"as a new week on the presidential campaign trail began","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"where the last one left off .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"We 're basically where we were on Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"when Romney said","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"he `` had no role whatsoever in the management of Bain Capital after February of 1999 ''","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and the Obama camp was arguing","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that public records indicate","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"he did .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"For his part , the president says","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"there 's no reason for him","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"to say","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"he 's sorry about ads","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"that are blasting Romney over the Bain connection .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"`` No , we will not apologize , ''","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"he told Virginia 's WAVY-TV .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"As FactCheck.org says ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"whether Romney was or was n't still involved in the running of Bain from 1999 into 2002 `` has become a key point of contention ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"because Obama TV ads accuse Romney of shipping U.S. jobs overseas . ''","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"That nonpartisan fact checking group has also reported","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that `` none of the SEC filings","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"[ cited by the Obama campaign as proof of Romney 's post-1999 involvement in Bain 's operations ]","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"show","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"that Romney was anything but a passive , absentee owner during that time ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"as both Romney and Bain have long said .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"It should not surprise anyone","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that Romney retained certain titles","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"while he was working out the final disposition of his ownership , for example . ''","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"`` Romney and his campaign have noted repeatedly","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that Romney left management of the company in 1999 .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"That may be ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"but Romney was the company 's founder ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"providing vision and direction for Bain .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"It 's not as if his influence ended the moment","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"he left","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"to run the Olympics . ''","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Still ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"says PolitiFact ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"`` calling the companies 'pioneers in outsourcing ' overstates the case .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"They did promote outsourcing ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"but they were part of a trend already decades in the making . ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"On Morning Edition today , NPR 's David Folkenflik broke down the brouhaha , the fact-checking and how the Romney campaign has handled the story .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":91,"left":90,"right":45,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":47,"right":89,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":47,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":51,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":51,"left":48,"right":50,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":48,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":50,"left":4,"right":49,"relation":"context","nuclearit